Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: The property is strategically located in the Golden Glades area of Miami Gardens, Florida and offers incredible transportation dynamics to move throughout South Florida and the state. The Golden Glades Interchange also serves as a East-West connector to many affluent areas such as Golden Beach, Aventura, Sunny Isles Beach, Surfside, Bal Harbour and North Beach. The property is accessible within a 15 minute drive to the residential neighborhoods of Hollywood and North Miami Beach.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: On behalf of the Owner, CBRE, Inc., as exclusive agent, is pleased to offer the Miami Gardens Corporate Headquarters located at 1160 NW 163rd Drive, Miami, Florida 33169 (“the property,” “building”, or “facility”), a 27,000 SF warehouse.  The facility is situated on ±1.33 acres of land with significant excess parking for storage, salesforce/employee parking or fleets. The building is serviced via multiple dock well and drive-in doors and is ideally setup for manufacturing, distribution and/or assembly.

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: Fronting the Palmetto Expressway, easily accessible ramps at NW 12th and NW 17th Avenues. Just west of Golden Glades Interchange, which connects to I-95, Florida's Turnpike, US441 (SR7), and Gratigny Expressway. Minutes to Hollywood / Fort Lauderdale, Aventura, Miami Lakes, Sunny Isles, and the beaches.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Secure building with many amenities on site.
